{
  "id": null,
  "uid": "otterworks-incident-overview",
  "title": "OtterWorks Incident Overview",
  "description": "Cross-service incident overview showing error rates, latencies, and active alerts across all OtterWorks services",
  "tags": [
    "otterworks",
    "incident",
    "overview"
  ],
  "timezone": "utc",
  "editable": true,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-30m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "datasource",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "current": {
          "text": "Prometheus",
          "value": "Prometheus"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "title": "Error Rates",
      "type": "row",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "title": "All Services - 5xx Error Rate",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 1
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "auto"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.01
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 0.05
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (job) (rate(http_requests_total{status=~\"5..\"}[5m])) / sum by (job) (rate(http_requests_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}}"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(search_service_requests_total{status=~\"5..\"}[5m])) / sum(rate(search_service_requests_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "search-service"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(notifications_processing_errors_total[5m])) / clamp_min(sum(rate(notifications_processing_errors_total[5m])) + 1, 1)",
          "legendFormat": "notification-service (consumer)"
        }
      ],
      "description": "5xx error rate for all services. A spike here indicates a service returning server errors."
    },
    {
      "title": "Latencies",
      "type": "row",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 9
      },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "title": "All Services - P95 Latency",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 10
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "min": 0,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "auto"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 1
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 3
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (job, le) (rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}}"
        }
      ],
      "description": "P95 latency across all services. A spike above 1s (warning) or 3s (critical) indicates performance degradation."
    },
    {
      "title": "Alerts and Diagnostics",
      "type": "row",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 18
      },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "title": "Active Alert Count",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 19
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 1
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 3
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "count(ALERTS{alertstate=\"firing\"}) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "Firing Alerts"
        }
      ],
      "description": "Total number of Prometheus alerts currently in firing state"
    },
    {
      "title": "Active Alerts Detail",
      "type": "table",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 16,
        "x": 8,
        "y": 19
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {}
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "ALERTS{alertstate=\"firing\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{alertname}} - {{job}}",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {
              "Time": true,
              "__name__": true,
              "Value": true
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "description": "Details of all currently firing alerts"
    },
    {
      "title": "Trace Search Links",
      "type": "row",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 25
      },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "title": "Jaeger Trace Search",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 26
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Trace Search by Service\n\nClick a service name to open Jaeger trace search filtered to that service:\n\n| Service | Language | Jaeger Link |\n|---------|----------|-------------|\n| api-gateway | Go | [Search Traces](http://jaeger:16686/search?service=api-gateway) |\n| auth-service | Java | [Search Traces](http://jaeger:16686/search?service=auth-service) |\n| file-service | Rust | [Search Traces](http://jaeger:16686/search?service=file-service) |\n| document-service | Python | [Search Traces](http://jaeger:16686/search?service=document-service) |\n| collab-service | Node.js | [Search Traces](http://jaeger:16686/search?service=collab-service) |\n| notification-service | Kotlin | [Search Traces](http://jaeger:16686/search?service=notification-service) |\n| search-service | Python | [Search Traces](http://jaeger:16686/search?service=search-service) |\n| analytics-service | Scala | [Search Traces](http://jaeger:16686/search?service=analytics-service) |\n| admin-service | Ruby | [Search Traces](http://jaeger:16686/search?service=admin-service) |\n| audit-service | C# | [Search Traces](http://jaeger:16686/search?service=audit-service) |"
      },
      "description": "Quick links to Jaeger trace search for each OtterWorks service"
    }
  ],
  "links": [
    {
      "title": "Chaos Scenarios",
      "url": "/d/otterworks-chaos-scenarios",
      "type": "link",
      "icon": "bolt",
      "tooltip": "View chaos engineering scenario dashboards"
    },
    {
      "title": "OtterWorks Overview",
      "url": "/d/otterworks-overview",
      "type": "link",
      "icon": "dashboard",
      "tooltip": "View high-level service overview"
    }
  ]
}
